{"tid":2289580,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"古仔低調賀余香凝大婚 狂被「集郵」","createTime":"2020-11-17T10:51:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-17T10:56:44.000Z","uid":156068,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b77e2509e5f49efa193f329520cb42e5f9d729c9","tid":2289580,"uid":156068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T10:51:56.000Z","msg":"盛傳雙喜臨門的余香凝（Jennifer）於上周六舉行婚禮，她所屬經理人公司老闆古天樂（古仔）都有親到現場祝賀一對新人，不過向來低調的古仔刻意經酒店後門入場，成功避過在酒店正門守候的大批傳媒。古仔在Jennifer的婚禮上當然成為一眾嘉賓的「集郵」目標，他亦來者不拒，開心與眾人合照，不少人在社交網晒「集郵」照，包括Jennifer的閨密廖子妤（fish），她笑言：「不是想擦鞋，只是想告白老闆，你這樣的打扮好帥。」她還問有沒有網友看過古仔的電影《乾柴烈火》。吳肇軒也趁上載社交網照片到達第1000張，大晒古仔合照，表示：「送上我與世上最帥的男人的合照。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zFaDbFa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzFaDbFa.jpg&h=c133d79f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bODYbFa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbODYbFa.jpg&h=f6bdda09&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bb81f69413707587e7daef14a16510dd1c5918e2","tid":2289580,"uid":238920,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T10:55:15.000Z","msg":"乜野叫想告白老闆?學埋晒d支那文法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想和老闆告白呢d小學雞造句都識啦"},{"pid":"d3d0891c7808f6fa45a0c3c06e076288a7d28834","tid":2289580,"uid":7947,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T10:56:09.000Z","msg":"地產仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />狐飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />魚哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />光軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"672f5785ecd03804dcb49810eed6ca34a66018c0","tid":2289580,"uid":7947,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d3d0891c7808f6fa45a0c3c06e076288a7d28834","tid":2289580,"uid":7947,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T10:56:09.000Z","msg":"地產仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=